::GoldenEye:;

She looked at him as he seamed to stare out into nothingness for a 
brief moment.  She smiled, "Well, both bases are realitively close. 
But it all depends on whom you wish to serve. Megatron ad his 
Predacons are in the forest on another continent."

She shifted her hips and stretched her wings behind her back and 
carefully fold them again.

"And then there is the other group. I haven't joined either one yet.  
I have been trying to find out which group may be more successful at 
winning the war. Although I think I have figure it out.  I'll have to 
let you decide on your own which one to join.  Myself, I will join 
the Allience."  

She looked at him again and smiled.  He was quite handsome. She 
wondered if he would follow her to the Pred base and join them as 
well.
